OL,3,CRupert Lowe sparks outrage after
OL,4,Cdescribing Dunblane tragedy as 'one
OL,5,Cmurder'
OL,7,FRupert Lowe has sparked outrage after
OL,8,Fincorrectly claiming there was just
OL,9,F"one murder" during the Dunblane
OL,10,Fmassacre.
OL,12,FThe Restore Britain leader told
OL,13,Fpodcaster Joe Rogan that handguns in
OL,14,Fthe UK were banned "because there was
OL,15,Fa murder up in Dunblane".
OL,17,FMr Rogan asks the Great Yarmouth MP:
OL,18,F"One murder?," before Mr Lowe replies:
OL,19,F"One murder."
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@LO]vD@TOUwD@XO]zD@AOUzD@NO]{D@
OL,26,AAOU{D@MO]
