OL,3,CRupert Lowe sparks outrage after
OL,4,Cdescribing Dunblane tragedy as 'one
OL,5,Cmurder'
OL,7,FSixteen children aged five and six and
OL,8,Ftheir teacher were killed by Thomas
OL,9,FHamilton at Dunblane Primary School on
OL,10,FMarch 13, 1996.
OL,12,FAnother 15 children and three adults
OL,13,Fwere injured before Hamilton killed
OL,14,Fhimself.
OL,16,FThe tragedy remains the deadliest mass
OL,17,Fshooting in British history and led to
OL,18,Fmajor reform of the UK's gun laws.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
