OL,3,CRupert Lowe sparks outrage after
OL,4,Cdescribing Dunblane tragedy as 'one
OL,5,Cmurder'
OL,7,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,8,Four political experts are across all
OL,9,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,10,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,12,FMr Lowe's comments prompted backlash,
OL,13,Fwith Scottish Conservative MSP Stephen
OL,14,FKerr describing them as "shocking".
OL,16,FHe said: "One murder? Sixteen kids and
OL,17,Ftheir teacher were murdered. Fifteen
OL,18,Fother primary school children were
OL,19,Fwounded.
OL,26,@vD@YOUvD@bO]xD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1783698492
OL,3,CRupert Lowe sparks outrage after
OL,4,Cdescribing Dunblane tragedy as 'one
OL,5,Cmurder'
OL,7,F"My children's school, about 15
OL,8,Fminutes from Dunblane, was locked down
OL,9,Fthat day. They'll never forget being
OL,10,Fkept in the gym hall until everyone
OL,11,Flearned the gunman was dead.
OL,13,F"They'll never forget the teachers
OL,14,Ftrying to hold themselves together
OL,15,Fwhile reassuring frightened children.
OL,17,F"To reduce that atrocity to 'one
OL,18,Fmurder' is deeply insulting. It wasn't
OL,19,Fa single murder. It was a mass murder.
OL,20,FIn a primary school."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
