CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1783698492
OL,3,CRupert Lowe sparks outrage after
OL,4,Cdescribing Dunblane tragedy as 'one
OL,5,Cmurder'
OL,7,FHe continued: "Almost as disturbing
OL,8,Fwas the tone ` one of disbelief, even
OL,9,Fmockery, that anyone could respond by
OL,10,Ftightening gun laws. This wasn't some
OL,11,Fobscure historical event. It happened
OL,12,Fin 1996, when Lowe was 38 years old.
OL,14,F"He should have known what happened on
OL,15,Fthat terrifying day in Dunblane. For
OL,16,Fanyone who remembers that day, hearing
OL,17,Fit dismissed so casually is genuinely
OL,18,Fshocking."
OL,26,@oD@OOUzD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
