OL,3,CRupert Lowe sparks outrage after
OL,4,Cdescribing Dunblane tragedy as 'one
OL,5,Cmurder'
OL,7,FMr Lowe made the comments as he gave
OL,8,Fhis opinion to Mr Rogan on why the UK
OL,9,Fhas strict gun laws.
OL,11,F"Effectively, they are trying to make
OL,12,Fthat very difficult through the
OL,13,Flicensing laws for guns," he said.
OL,15,F"My father used to shoot pistols for
OL,16,FOxford University and he's dead now,
OL,17,Fbless him, but all his pistols were
OL,18,Ftaken away, the pistols he used to
OL,19,Fshoot with at Oxford University.
OL,26,@sD@AOUuD@YO]wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31107
