OL,3,CRupert Lowe sparks outrage after
OL,4,Cdescribing Dunblane tragedy as 'one
OL,5,Cmurder'
OL,7,F"I mean, we now have a society which
OL,8,Fneeds radical change."
OL,10,FClackmannanshire and Dunblane SNP MSP
OL,11,FKeith Brown said: "Rupert Lowe is a
OL,12,Fstain on our politics and his comments
OL,13,Fare beyond despicable. Sixteen
OL,14,Fchildren and a teacher were shot dead
OL,15,Fwhile 15 more children were wounded.
OL,26,@pD@VO]sD@SOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
