OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1783698492
OL,3,CRupert Lowe sparks outrage after
OL,4,Cdescribing Dunblane tragedy as 'one
OL,5,Cmurder'
OL,7,F"Despite these hideous remarks from
OL,8,FRupert Lowe, the Snowdrop Campaign
OL,9,Fthat followed that terrible day
OL,10,Fensured a ban on the private ownership
OL,11,Fof most handguns ` that is the proud
OL,12,Flegacy of the bereaved families and
OL,13,Fthe local community.
OL,15,F"Their courage and determination in
OL,16,Fthe aftermath of the attack is
OL,17,Fsomething we should never betray and
OL,18,Four community will never let the likes
OL,19,Fof Rupert Lowe do exactly that."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU{D@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
