OL,3,CRupert Lowe sparks outrage after
OL,4,Cdescribing Dunblane tragedy as 'one
OL,5,Cmurder'
OL,7,FLabour MP Chris Kane raised a point of
OL,8,Forder in the House of Commons, telling
OL,9,FMPs Mr Lowe's comments had "caused
OL,10,Fprofound offence to the community" in
OL,11,Fhis Stirling and Strathallan
OL,12,Fconstituency.
OL,14,F"To describe the Dunblane tragedy as
OL,15,F'one murder' diminishes what happened
OL,16,Fto 16 children and their teacher, and
OL,17,Fthe suffering of everyone whose lives
OL,18,Fwere changed forever in March 1996,"
OL,19,Fhe said.
OL,26,@qD@\OUrD@bO]vD@AOUzD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
