OL,3,CRupert Lowe sparks outrage after
OL,4,Cdescribing Dunblane tragedy as 'one
OL,5,Cmurder'
OL,7,F"It is because of their courage and
OL,8,Fthe united action of this House that
OL,9,Fthis country has some of the strongest
OL,10,Ffirearms laws in the world, and an
OL,11,Fongoing cross-party approach to
OL,12,Fensuring these protections will not be
OL,13,Fweakened."
OL,15,FThe Dunblane massacre shocked the
OL,16,Fnation and led to the UK enforcing
OL,17,Fsome of the strictest firearms
OL,18,Flegislation in the world.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@JO]
