OL,3,CRupert Lowe sparks outrage after
OL,4,Cdescribing Dunblane tragedy as 'one
OL,5,Cmurder'
OL,7,FIn the wake of outrage and anti-gun
OL,8,Fcampaigning after the atrocity, a ban
OL,9,Fon most handguns was introduced by
OL,10,FJohn Major's Conservative government
OL,11,Fin 1997.
OL,13,FLater that year, legislation widening
OL,14,Fthe ban to include all cartridge
OL,15,Fammunition handguns was introduced by
OL,16,FTony Blair's Labour government.
OL,18,FA Restore Britain spokesman said:
OL,19,F"Rupert was clearly referring to one
OL,20,Fincident."
